985. Brain. 2019 Dec 1;142(12):3876-3891. doi: 10.1093/brain/awz326.

Biallelic DMXL2 mutations impair autophagy and cause Ohtahara syndrome with 
progressive course.

Esposito A(1)(2), Falace A(3), Wagner M(4)(5)(6), Gal M(7), Mei D(3), Conti 
V(3), Pisano T(3), Aprile D(2), Cerullo MS(1)(2), De Fusco A(1)(2), Giovedì 
S(2), Seibt A(8), Magen D(9)(10), Polster T(11), Eran A(9)(12), Stenton 
SL(4)(5), Fiorillo C(13)(14), Ravid S(9)(15), Mayatepek E(8), Hafner H(9)(16), 
Wortmann S(4)(5)(17), Levanon EY(7), Marini C(3), Mandel H(9)(18), Benfenati 
F(1)(19), Distelmaier F(8), Fassio A(2)(19), Guerrini R(3)(20).

