Metastatic Spine Disease: Should Patients With Short Life Expectancy Be Denied 
Surgical Care? An International Retrospective Cohort Study.

Dea N(1), Versteeg AL(2), Sahgal A(3), Verlaan JJ(2), Charest-Morin R(1), Rhines 
